OP12-OP12-001 normal.name: Silvers Rayleigh
OP12-OP12-001 normal.description:
Under the rules of this game, you cannot include cards with a cost of 5 or more in your deck.
[Activate: Main] [Once Per Turn] You may reveal 2 Events from your hand: Up to 1 of your Characters with 4000 base power or less gains +2000 power during this turn.

OP12-OP12-006 normal.name: Shakuyaku
OP12-OP12-006 normal.description: [On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 1 [Monkey.D.Luffy] or 1 red Event and add it to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.

OP12-OP12-008 normal.name: Shanks (008)
OP12-OP12-008 normal.description:
[Blocker]
[On Your Opponent's Attack] [Once Per Turn] You may trash 1 card from your hand: Give up to 1 of your opponent's Leader or Character cards 2000 power during this turn.

OP12-OP12-009 normal.name: Jinbe
OP12-OP12-009 normal.description: [On Play] You may reveal 2 Events from your hand: This Character gains [Rush] during this turn. Then, this Character gains +1000 power until the end of your opponent's next End Phase.

OP12-OP12-018 normal.name: Color of the Supreme King Haki
OP12-OP12-018 normal.description: [Counter] Up to 1 of your Characters or [Silvers Rayleigh] gains +2000 power during this battle. Then, you may rest 1 of your DON!! cards. If you do, give your opponent's Leader and all of their Characters 1000 power during this turn.

OP12-OP12-020 normal.name: Roronoa Zoro (020)
OP12-OP12-020 normal.description: [DON!! x3] [Activate: Main] [Once Per Turn] If this Leader battles your opponent's Character during this turn, set this Leader as active. Then, this Leader cannot attack your opponent's Characters with a base cost of 7 or less during this turn.

OP12-OP12-031 normal.name: Tashigi
OP12-OP12-031 normal.description: [On Play] Rest up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a base cost of 6 or less. Then, give up to 3 rested DON!! cards to your [Roronoa Zoro] Leader.

OP12-OP12-037 normal.name: Demon Aura Nine Sword Style Asura Blades Drawn Dead Man's Game
OP12-OP12-037 normal.description:
[Main] You may rest 3 of your DON!! cards: Rest up to a total of 2 of your opponent's Characters or DON!! cards.
[Counter] Your Leader gains +3000 power during this battle.

OP12-OP12-039 normal.name: Luffy Is the Man Who Will Become the King of Pirates!!!
OP12-OP12-039 normal.description:
[Main] Set your [Roronoa Zoro] Leader as active.
[Trigger] Up to 1 of your Leader or Character cards gains +1000 power during this turn.

OP12-OP12-040 normal.name: Kuzan (040)
OP12-OP12-040 normal.description: When a card is trashed from your hand by your "Navy" type card's effect, draw cards equal to the number of cards trashed.

OP12-OP12-041 normal.name: Sanji (041)
OP12-OP12-041 normal.description:
[Activate: Main] [Once Per Turn] DON!! 1: Activate up to 1 "Straw Hat Crew" type Event with a base cost of 3 or less from your hand.
[When Attacking] If the number of DON!! cards on your field is equal to or less than the number on your opponent's field, add up to 1 DON!! card from your DON!! deck and rest it.

OP12-OP12-043 normal.name: Kuzan (043)
OP12-OP12-043 normal.description:
If you have 5 or more cards in your hand, this Character gains +1 cost.
[On Play] You may trash 1 card from your hand: Up to 1 of your opponent's Characters cannot attack until the end of your opponent's next End Phase.

OP12-OP12-044 normal.name: Sakazuki
OP12-OP12-044 normal.description:
[On Play] If your Leader has the "Navy" type, draw 2 cards.
[Activate: Main] [Once Per Turn] You may trash 1 card from your hand: Give up to 1 rested DON!! card to your Leader or 1 of your Characters.

OP12-OP12-047 normal.name: Sengoku
OP12-OP12-047 normal.description: [On Play] You may trash 1 card from your hand: Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 2 "Navy" type cards other than [Sengoku] and add them to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.

OP12-OP12-053 normal.name: Borsalino
OP12-OP12-053 normal.description:
[Once Per Turn] If this Character would be removed from the field by your opponent's effect, you may trash 1 card from your hand instead.
[Opponent's Turn] If your Leader has the "Navy" type, this Character gains [Blocker] and +1000 power.

OP12-OP12-060 normal.name: Boeuf Burst
OP12-OP12-060 normal.description:
[Main] If your Leader is multicolored, choose one:
• Return up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a cost of 4 or less to the owner's hand.
• If you have 6 or less cards in your hand, draw 2 cards.

OP12-OP12-061 normal.name: Donquixote Rosinante (061)
OP12-OP12-061 normal.description:
[Once Per Turn] If your [Trafalgar Law] would be K.O.'d, you may add 1 card from the top of your Life cards to your hand instead.
[Activate: Main] [Once Per Turn] DON!! 1: The next time you play [Trafalgar Law] with a cost of 4 or more from your hand during this turn, the cost will be reduced by 2.

OP12-OP12-070 normal.name: Sanji (070)
OP12-OP12-070 normal.description:
This Character gains +1000 power for every 5 Events in your trash.
If this Character would be removed from the field by your opponent's effect, you may return 1 DON!! card from your field to your DON!! deck instead.

OP12-OP12-079 normal.name: Luffy Is the Man Who Will Be King of the Pirates!!!
OP12-OP12-079 normal.description: [Main] If your Leader is [Sanji], look at 3 cards from the top of your deck and add up to 1 card to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.

OP12-OP12-081 normal.name: Koala (081)
OP12-OP12-081 normal.description:
When this Leader attacks your opponent's Leader, if you have 2 or more Characters with a cost of 8 or more, draw 1 card.
[Once Per Turn] This effect can be activated when your opponent plays a Character with a base cost of 8 or more, or when your opponent plays a Character using a Character's effect. Your opponent adds 1 card from the top of their Life cards to their hand.

OP12-OP12-086 normal.name: Koala (086)
OP12-OP12-086 normal.description: [On Play] If your Leader has the "Revolutionary Army" type, look at 3 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 1 "Revolutionary Army" type card other than [Koala] or up to 1 [Nico Robin] and add it to your hand. Then, trash the rest.

OP12-OP12-089 normal.name: Hack
OP12-OP12-089 normal.description:
If your Leader has the "Revolutionary Army" type, this Character gains [Blocker] and +4 cost.
[On K.O.] If your Leader has the "Revolutionary Army" type, K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a base cost of 4 or less.

OP12-OP12-097 normal.name: Captains Assembled
OP12-OP12-097 normal.description:
[Main] Look at 3 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 1 "Revolutionary Army" type card other than [Captains Assembled] and add it to your hand. Then, trash the rest.
[Trigger] Activate this card's [Main] effect.

OP12-OP12-100 normal.name: Sabo
OP12-OP12-100 normal.description:
If you have 3 or less Life cards, this Character gains [Blocker] and +3 cost.
[On Play] You may add 1 card from the top of your Life cards to your hand: Draw 2 cards and trash 1 card from your hand.

OP12-OP12-107 normal.name: Donquixote Doflamingo
OP12-OP12-107 normal.types: Donquixote Pirates;The Seven Warlords of the Sea
OP12-OP12-107 normal.description:
If you have 2 or less Life cards, this Character gains [Rush].
(This card can attack on the turn in which it is played.)
[Opponent's Turn] [On K.O.] Add up to 1 card from the top of your deck to the top of your Life cards.

OP12-OP12-108 normal.name: Donquixote Rosinante (108)
OP12-OP12-108 normal.description: [On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 1 [Trafalgar Law] and add it to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.

OP12-OP12-112 normal.name: Baby 5 (112)
OP12-OP12-112 normal.description: [Trigger] If your Leader is multicolored, draw 2 cards.

OP12-OP12-118 normal.name: Jewelry Bonney (118)
OP12-OP12-118 normal.description:
[Blocker]
[On Play] If you have 8 or more rested cards, draw 2 cards and trash 1 card from your hand. Then, set up to 1 of your DON!! cards as active.

OP12-OP12-119 normal.name: Bartholomew Kuma
OP12-OP12-119 normal.types: Revolutionary Army;The Seven Warlords of the Sea
OP12-OP12-119 normal.description:
[On Play] You may trash 1 card from your hand: Add up to 1 card from the top of your deck to the top of your Life cards. Then, this Character gains +2 cost until the end of your opponent's next End Phase.
[Opponent's Turn] [On K.O.] Add up to 1 card from the top of your deck to the top of your Life cards.
